headline: AT&T price target raised to $26 from $24 at Citi
summary: Citi raised the firm’s price target on AT&T to $26 from $24 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares ahead of the investor day on December 3. The firm expects an update on AT&T’s multi-year strategy, financial prospects, and capital allocation priorities, and continues to view the event as a potentially positive catalyst for the shares.
